$ Standard C library: stdarg.h

{ In conjuntion with vsprintf #libc-stdarg-h-vsprintf

  `<stdarg.h>` in conjunction with `vsprintf` allows to write a → development/languages/printf[`printf`] function that automatically prepends the written string with a timestamp:

  gh|about-libc|/stdarg.h/vsprintf/prog.c||

